///   propagate or break out. It's the replacement for the ThreadAbortException
///   pattern but is NOT auto-rethrown like ThreadAbortException was.
///
/// • Dispose CancellationTokenSource. It's IDisposable and holds a
///   WaitHandle internally.
///
